            "width": 1500
          }
        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Chop your <strong>cod fillet[s]</strong> into large, bite-sized pieces, then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Drain your <strong>king prawns</strong>,<strong> </strong>then pat dry with kitchen paper</p><p>Sprinkle a little <strong>flour</strong> over the <strong>chopped cod</strong> and <strong>king prawns</strong>, then toss until lightly floured</p>",
      "order": 2,
      "media": {
        "images": [
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1689685518416-x200.jpg",
            "width": 200
          },
          {
            "image": "https://production-media.gousto.co.uk/cms/recipe-step-image/step-2-1689685518416-x400.jpg",
