        ]
      }
    },
    {
      "instruction": "<p>Wash your <strong>spinach</strong></p><p>Add the<strong> spinach</strong> and <strong>blanched peas</strong> to a colander and pour <strong>boiled water</strong> all over them to refresh them</p><p>Combine the <strong>refreshed spinach </strong>and<strong> peas</strong> with 1 tsp <span class=\"text-purple\">[1 1/2 tsp]</span> <span class=\"text-danger\">[2 tsp]</span> <strong>butter</strong> and a pinch of <strong>salt </strong>– this is your<strong> buttered veg</strong></p>",
      "order": 7,
